What is #TidyTuesday?
========================================================

- is a hashtag used on twitter
- twitter > important
- a project by the R4DS community $\to$ http://www.rfordatasci.com/
- a weekly visualisation project: https://github.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday
- addresses the need in learning the tidyverse ecosystem, having a small ...+ some kind of template
- started in April
- data released on monday, work on tuesday, publish on twitter. 

